# Admin app

- **Purpose:** Internal Traverum platform admin. Hotel payouts management, partner list, "Open in dashboard" for superadmin support. Not for customers.
- **Stack:** Vite + React SPA (same as dashboard). No Next.js. Supabase client (anon key); RLS gives superadmins access via `get_user_partner_ids()`.
- **Access:** Only users with `users.is_superadmin = true` can use the app; `SuperadminGuard` enforces this after auth.
- **Env:** All config is build-time: `VITE_SUPABASE_URL`, `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY`, `VITE_DASHBOARD_URL`, `VITE_WIDGET_API_URL`. See `docs/deployment/ADMIN_VERCEL_DEPLOYMENT.md`.
- **Deployment:** Separate Vercel project; Root Directory must be `apps/admin`. Uses `npx vite build` directly (not `pnpm --filter`) to avoid OOM on Vercel Hobby. Never deploy dashboard or widget from this root. See `docs/deployment/VERCEL_DEPLOYMENTS.md`.
